<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Lov min Gud</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bless the Lord, oh my soul
 and all that is within me
 Bless His Holy Name! (2x)

[V2]
 For He has done great things
 He has done great things
 He has done great things
 Bless His Holy Name!

[V3]
 Lov min Gud, å min sjel,
 og alt som i meg finnes,
 pris Hans Hellige Navn. (2x)

[V4]
 For Han har gjort så store ting,
 Han har gjort så store ting,
 Han har gjort så store ting,
 Pris Hans Hellige Navn.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Bless the Lord</title>
<presentation>v1 v2 v3 v4 </presentation>
</song>